'''Afullus''' (tawtmt nns : '''Tafullust''') iga yan anaw n [[Agḍiḍ|igḍaḍ]] idusn ifulkin, ar itzdaɣ d ufgan ɣ tgmmi nns. Iga yan wanaw nna bahra nctta acku tifiyya nns tmmim.

==Assaɣ==
Irwas iz awal ad n Afullus illa ɣar ɣ tutlayt [[taclḥit]], ɣ [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] yaḍni zund [[taqbaylit]] d [[tarifit]] ar nttafa ''Ayaziḍ'' nɣ ''Yaziḍ''.<ref>[http://amawal.net/ayazi%E1%B8%8D?action=rpx_token&l=fr_FR Ayaziḍ] - Amawal.net</ref>

Nzḍar ad nbḍu awal ad n Afullus s sin n tguriwin atnt igan : A + Fullus

Awal ad n Afullus illa ula ɣ tutlayt [[Tutlayt Talatint|talatint tazaykut]], ulla nttni ɛnan sis nit afullus, awal ad iga tt ''Pullus'', ɣid ar nttafa mas ittuysnfl F s P. D A lli llan ɣ umzwaru n tguri ar aɣ tmmal mas awal ad iga mudakar, zund [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] kullutn abla [[tarifit]].

Illa mad ak ittinin maḥd tutlayin timaziɣin yaḍni ar ttinin Ayaziḍ han ḥaqqan is Afullus ikka d [[Tutlayt Talatint|talatint]]. Mac ur nzḍar ad nssn manta gisn ad yussin tguri zɣ ṭayya acku ur illi ḥtta yan uɣbalu nna fllas isawln.

