==Anawn n ifullusn : ==
*'''Afullus abldi''' : igat ufullus n tgmmi.
*'''Afullus aṛumi''' : igat ufullus umlil inzzan g tḥanut, ar yakka tifyyi.
*'''Afullus akrwaẓi''' : igat ufullus yakkan tiglay nzzanin g tḥanut.

